<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">那么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古代究竟有没有轻功呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了环保</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此处省略1万字论证过程</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201014/edc8622d1d6e475a8eb9931e9f160e30.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201014/2a526aac88254d4ebff40e13d585088e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">轻功绝对不是超能力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是内功大法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更不是气功大法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这是一门技术</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201014/bbb941f774d8427999fcb08cb5ec523b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201014/32c706b0d09b4078a5ea166d0dc2db7c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">钻洞技术1</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">借力卸力</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201014/fc9aef4488694e658ea2de67cf014ca6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对于轻功</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《北史》</strong>有比较靠谱的记载</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寺庙里旗幡杆上的绳索断了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">接不上去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>沈光</strong>看见后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嘴里衔着绳索，揭竿而上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接跳到旗杆顶端去接绳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古人以为他是内力发功</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还把跳高称之为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>轻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>功</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201014/0562f7abe536483e94161973028adb18.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沈光跟着<strong>隋炀帝</strong>去棒子国打仗时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被敌兵推下了城墙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正好碰到<strong>云梯</strong>上垂下的绳索</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是沈光发挥<strong>撑杆跳高才能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抓住绳索翻身</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又攀上城墙与敌兵厮杀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">观战的隋炀帝对沈光的飞檐走壁十分惊讶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说白了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沈光的飞檐走壁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是<strong>借力腾空</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201014/9de3fbcc30794cbda3ea47221d7dd52d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到了电视里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就成了飞檐走壁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不用杆子和绳子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>凌空跳出了十几层楼高</strong>的效果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201014/a9894003147c40e3a14e6e53777f4b3a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201014/f12cf0b34e354f6797bec1dde9dad450.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这种借力腾空的轻功</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不够仙气飘飘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古人就<strong>借药腾空</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长沙<strong>马王堆汉墓</strong>里出土过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“疾行方”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是古代的<strong>兴奋剂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据说吃了能让人瞬间拥有轻功</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（其实只是道士们的心理安慰）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201014/dcdaf781187648618dc5af889b98b1e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201014/2d8eff47fecd454093f4d3b50fbee889.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现代习武之人用兴奋剂是<strong>可耻的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们还是老老实实<strong>物理借力卸力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让自己轻如飞燕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如<strong>轻功踩蛋蛋生鸡蛋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201014/0943d588c3874c38b1880d47d1e75f4a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现实中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人双脚踩在两排蛋上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蛋也能一个不碎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201014/4fdd7b559f384b1c843f00ba5e2946bb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">江湖骗子都号称自己是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>——内力发功，让体重变轻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">网络鉴假师一口咬定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要么<strong>百万剪辑</strong>要么绝对是<strong>生鸡蛋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们只是偷偷穿了一双<strong>软底胶鞋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将<strong>放在蛋上的力均匀扩散</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201014/0f60949c5120400b806de4df2d5e1da5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>大多数轻功是使用了借力卸力的钻漏洞技巧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飞檐走壁就是一套行走的物理公式</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">草上飞的草</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鼓上蚤的鼓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水上飘的水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梯云纵好比乔丹的滞空拉杆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凌波微步好比吉诺比利的欧洲步上篮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——而不是玄学里的内力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201014/3b4ffa16df57485e9f5c377d515559ca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但人的肌肉爆发力有限</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">根本不可能像武侠小说那样跳20层楼高</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除非你是一只<strong>中华田园猫</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201014/40d9ea9e0d1c4bd8b48c650e14598cd8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">钻洞技术2</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">平衡力</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">比沈光撑杆跳高更让古人惊讶的轻功</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是禅宗祖师——<strong>达摩</strong>的<strong>一苇渡江</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他在江边折了一根<strong>芦苇</strong>投入江中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后站在芦苇上<strong>飘然过江</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八仙过海不过如此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别人以为他的芦苇跟平常吃的芦苇一样小</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实他的芦苇<strong>又大又厚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>站下两个人绰绰有余</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201014/5544ea2b94604f0cbc9aa15eb28cb80b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加上达摩的<strong>平衡能力特别好</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以能踏着芦苇渡江</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并不是使用超能力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这种轻功</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贵州的大爷大妈也能整一出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">称为<strong>独竹飘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201014/ce6240b453724d148aba427b1e44f895.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201014/6aa9b26332ab47239b01173438550e57.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大爷大妈们脚踩一根<strong>楠竹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在水上漂来漂去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果远看就看不到竹子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人就像在<strong>水上飞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201014/dc6d58d9a4a34abe819550b6599b7763.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">轻功水上漂、踏雪无痕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也跟气功和内力无关</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是<strong>动态平衡力的掌控</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就好比体操和跑酷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">汉朝美女<strong>赵飞燕</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据说会气功和轻功，身轻如燕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以在太监掌中起舞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这也是<strong>文学夸张手法</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只能说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传统舞蹈能控制身体重心，掌握平衡的技术</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">跟轻功差不多了</p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">钻洞技术3</h1>
<h1 class="ql-align-center">惯性的力量</h1>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了借力卸力和平衡力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>牛顿的惯性</strong>也是一个好东西</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是在钻牛顿最大的漏洞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>冲拳可折断筷子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201014/957a27ff37ac4141a8825ac8bc2e3f04.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">单凭一只手要折断筷子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并没有力可以借</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果不是<strong>掰断</strong>和<strong>剪辑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玄学爱好者又认为是内力在发功</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">运用用一根杠杆就可以撬动地球的原理</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">手握在100克筷子的<strong>三分之一</strong>处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出拳速度足够快，<strong>每秒10米</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">快到拳头都收回来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为惯性</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三分之二的筷子还<strong>没反应过来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就落单在空中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后<strong>断开</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201014/db8ddb87361b44fc9a3809263b78a300.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在许多人眼里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既然内力和气功不可靠就——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>万物皆可丹田</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据说人体主要的丹田在肚子里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要看一个人能不能练轻功</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅是看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201014/229f3b7e7199403aba48cc9e88d99deb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还要看——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201014/d49092112a224578a651ce29a8f626e4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是你连丹田都不想练</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你可以求助<strong>物理食物的力量</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实现轻功水上漂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">做非牛顿流体</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你可以<strong>在水里加入足量的淀粉</strong>（比例约 2∶1）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">做成非牛顿流体</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201014/5af66b6a1f06450ba016599ffad29907.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这种流体<strong>受力越迅勐，质地越坚硬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你在上面缓步行走</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很快就会<strong>陷下去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但如果撒丫子狂奔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">反而会<strong>如履平地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201014/929c6379e26a4712b71bc01ee2ecc9b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201014/409204003fa5445eafd301e41d1fd042.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这淀粉水上飘还是需要物理常识</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱卿一提到物理就头疼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201014/31b1a5d77c1d4f409ea6a07ddef8fb55.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">轻功练的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>平衡力、弹跳力、借力、</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>黄桑的男友力、阻挡死神的死皮赖脸能力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是你只练物理常识</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不练<strong>跑步、跑桩、跑砖、竖立砖、顶功……</strong>等技巧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就想毫无痕迹地展示自己白气飘飘的样子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（简称白嫖）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那物理科学家和物理老师</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人人皆少林武侠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201014/d468dcb3deed4fa9a8f0f499acad578d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不练功也可以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是你连物理食物都弄不来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就想做一个轻功高手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（说到底还是想白嫖！）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕只能说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>好好蹲坑吧！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起码能做一只</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>便</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>健</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>康</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>咸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鱼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201014/a258d9831fc248f2b12f47dde7fabb21.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本文系【朕说】原创内容</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">未经账号授权，禁止随意转载</p>